data.description:
Inviting Home with a lot of Square Footage in this Unique Floor Plan. Master, Master Bath, Laundry and Garage all on the Main Floor. Oversized Family Room with Gas Log Fireplace. Large Eat in Kitchen That Looks Out Over the Patio. Also a Formal Dining Room and Half Bath.
Upstairs has Three More Bedrooms and Second Full Bath with a landing for a desk. Lower Level Is a Huge Surprise: Media/Rec Room with Second Gas Log Fireplace, Kitchenette, Three More Rooms that Can be Used as Non-Conforming Bedrooms/Offices and a Third Full Bath. Some fun little nuggets like Laundry Drop, Outside Basketball Pad, Central Vacuum, Tons of Closets.
